comments.text:
JAM with Chrome is an interactive web application that allows friends in 
different locations to play music together in real time through their 
Chrome browser, using the latest HTML5 technologies. You can choose from 
one of 19 instruments and up to 4 people can JAM together in a session. To 
start your own JAM session visit jamwithchrome.com﻿
